---
import BaseLayout from '../../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
    title="The Halo Effect: Attracting Tech Ecosystems | TomorrowBeginsHere.com"
    description="Learn how a data center campus acts as a primary anchor, attracting secondary employers and seeding a regional technology ecosystem."
>
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="bg-slate-900 border-b border-tech-blue/20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-950/80 via-slate-900/95 to-tech-blue/80 z-0 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/texas-data-centers-network.png')] bg-cover bg-center z-0 opacity-15 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-24 text-center">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-violet-500/20 text-violet-300 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-6 border border-violet-500/30 backdrop-blur-sm">Pillar 06 • The Halo Effect</span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
                The Halo Effect:<br><span class="text-violet-300">Anchor Infrastructure for What's Next</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
                A data center isn't just a single commercial building—it is a digital foundation that transforms a county into a premier regional technology destination.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white relative">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
                
                <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-800 font-semibold mb-8">
                    A data center is not just one building. It is an anchor.
                </p>

                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Modern companies want to set up where strong digital infrastructure already exists. Once a campus is here, it puts our community on the map for the next employer, and the developers often bring new power and new water systems with them.
                </p>
 
                 <!-- Halo Effect Showcase Card -->
                 <div class="bg-violet-50 border border-violet-200 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 my-12 shadow-sm">
                     <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-violet-950 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                         <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-violet-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                             <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                         </svg>
                         Upgraded Utility Backbones at Zero Taxpayer Cost
                     </h3>
                     <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                         To build a data center, developers must invest millions of dollars of private capital into regional utility connections. These improvements are fully financed by the developers but often benefit the surrounding community:
                     </p>
                     <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600 mb-0">
                         <li>• **High-Capacity Fiber loops** that improve regional broadband reliability for residents.</li>
                         <li>• **Water main upgrades** and wastewater infrastructure extensions.</li>
                         <li>• **Electrical substations** that reinforce power distribution for nearby business parks.</li>
                     </ul>
                 </div>

                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-lg font-medium">
                    This is how a county positions itself for the businesses of the future instead of getting left behind.
                </p>

                <hr class="border-slate-200 my-12">

                <div class="text-center bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-bold">Explore the next pillar</p>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Pillar 07: Construction & Jobs — Keeping the Workforce Busy</h4>
                    <a href="/texas-data-centers/construction-jobs" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-6 py-3 bg-tech-blue hover:bg-tech-blue/90 text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors">
                        Next: Construction Jobs
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
